title: Prassi ONES Optical New Edge Storage v2.1.358 RETAIL
description:
PRASSI ONES has been designed to meet the needs of both beginners and experienced users alike, thanks to its intuitive and user-friendly interface. ONES is different from other CD/DVD burning software as it uses an innovative new recording technology which means that it can function with any existing or future CD/DVD recorder. Updates are no longer necessary. 
ONES is fully compatible with Windows Vista
